Package com.werdpressed.partisan.rundo

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RunDo.ErrorHandlingCallback
    Implement for custom error handling if IndexOutOfBoundsException encountered when calling RunDo.undo() or RunDo.redo().
    RunDo.UndoRedoCallbacks
    Provides callbacks whenever RunDo.undo() and RunDo.redo() methods are called.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomArrayDeque<T>
    Implementation of ArrayDeque class that adds a fixed, maximum capacity.
    RunDo
    Adds Undo/Redo functions to either an instance of, or a class that inherits from, EditText

    Implementation will often simply be a case of instantiating a RunDo object, passing an EditText argument and calling RunDo.undo() and RunDo.redo() methods.
    SubtractStrings
    Compares two String objects and returns the first and last points they deviate from one another, subStrings between the two, and information on whether or not text has been added, replaced or deleted.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RunDo.TrackingState
    Tracks whether the user is currently typing (CURRENT), whether user has finished typing and tracking is ready to restart (ENDED), or whether user has finished typing but tracking is not yet ready to begin (STARTED).
